0Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"77d41a113a8d0aadcae38822bf9545a601324d24","tid":1346574,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:37:40.000Z","msg":"老百姓自衛殺死黑社會不犯法<br />\n<br />\n【警方通報&ldquo;昆山砍人案&rdquo;：騎車男不負刑事責任 撤銷該案】<br />\n<br />\n江蘇昆山，寶馬男追砍電動車主遭反殺引發熱議。今日，昆山公安通報稱：電動車主於海明的行為屬於正當防衛，不負刑事責任，公安機關依法撤銷於海明案件。"},{"pid":"91f00482eba8b0fe9acf83b40c29170e78bc821e","tid":1346574,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:37:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9101afb6c1744f6ec8bcbd69e1e7f181a113050","tid":1346574,"uid":265904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:38:42.000Z","msg":"何君堯都話唔會割蓆!!!!!大家加油!!"},{"pid":"d3d46856a0e71bcbf168d03516266bb336d54e1f","tid":1346574,"uid":99243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:39:17.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"e26cc202b7a0e4c0f7919f6c73e37a34239d1ef1","tid":1346574,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:39:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一、</span></span><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以群眾鬥群眾</span></ins></strong>，內耗消耗民意，<br />\n引起眾多火頭，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>燃起多條戰綫，力圖模糊最初目標</ins></strong></span>，<br />\n大家要諗諗點拆<br />\n<br />\n或者好似另外一啲巴絲講，<br />\n陰謀論諗，可能借無差別攻擊事件自製亂象，繼而自己修補亂象，<br />\n繼而挽回民望<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">二、</span></span>另外大家可以 brainstorm 下：dress code 以顏色區分是否繼續可行？<br />\n如果著 smart casual 恤衫返工裝，<br />\n人人都係打工仔，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><strong>人人都係 water</strong></ins></span>，<br />\n到時打，打打工仔，打平民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三、</span></span>除 TVB 有免費 24 小時電視新聞頻道外，<br />\nViuTV 同奇妙電視應該要同樣加開免費 24 小時電視新聞頻道，<br />\n本身兩台已有班底，只須加開頻道即可<br />\n甚至可考慮<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全港首創本地 24 小時英語新聞頻道</span></ins></strong><br />\nRTHK 31 亦要加強推廣自身頻道<br />\n<br />\n同溫層講，大家都識得睇其他新聞，<br />\n但須知道好多酒樓、食肆冇嘢好播，咪播 TVB 新聞，<br />\n上年紀一輩只識打開對眼就睇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">四、</span></span>同樣唔可以忽視就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><strong>境外酒店電視落地</strong></ins></span>，<br />\n大家打開酒店電視，睇香港嘅頻道，只會搵到 TVB，得 TVB 落到地，<br />\n呢方面要大家諗諗<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>（外地人士第一觀感）</ins></strong></span>"},{"pid":"457bffcc4689d82123fdf9de3d30e21a6a90e809","tid":1346574,"uid":230511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:40:33.000Z","msg":"間狗屋著火都唔會割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cdde48a6543f870a99427b91288321c21f459a6","tid":1346574,"uid":239250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:52:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fbae5601d5488142b8f7f948ee1060e622863023","tid":1346574,"uid":6594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:09:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">永不割蓆</span></span>"},{"pid":"fa168b72d4929914d541ce22c12573190e482aa4","tid":1346574,"uid":54663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:12:31.000Z","msg":"永不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"}]}